## Wiki

This wiki has been setup as part of a documentation effort around [[bitcoin]]. You can [learn more about MediaWiki formatting](http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting). Should you want to start the wiki in your own language, you can make a request by [email](mailto:contact@bitcoin.it).

Backups are [available](https://dump.bitcoin.it/) and anyone is welcome to download them and mirror this wiki.

This wiki is available in more than one language. When a given page is available in another language, a link on the left will be displayed for each available language.

